title: ELEMENT MAKE IT COUNT: PORTUGAL 2015
description:
Congrats to DUARTE POMBO who won the MAKE IT COUNT contest in Viseu, Portugal!
Duarte won a spot in the European Finals that will take place in Italy and a chance to win a trip to California to compete for Element sponsorship at Nyjah's park!
